
=pod

=head1 History revision for DiCoP-Base

This document details the complete changes from v3.01 onwards.

See the CHANGES-3.01 file and the CHANGES files in the DiCoP-Server package
for the full version history.

=head2 2006-06-01 (Base v3.03)

=over 2

=item fixed

	rmoved unused uptime() hook for output
	fix all POD errors and add POD tests
	bring POD coverage to 100% and test for it
	wcr lib: Total: lines 8851, words 31397, chars 225268
	1538 tests

=back

=head2 2006-05-03 (Base v3.02)

No functional changes:

=over 2

=item fixed

	require Math::BigInt v1.77
	Makefile.PL: use YAML to generate better META.yml
	Makefile.PL: use PREREQ_FATAL
	call output() with $self as first param when not being able to load
	  Linux::Cpuinfo
	fix (c) dates, contact address etc
	make a non-beta version for release
	add a SIGNATURE again (for CPAN release)
	wcr lib: Total: lines 8734, words 30983, chars 222455
	1499 tests

=back

=head2 2005-04-20 (Base v3.01 build 3)

=over 2

=item fixed

	require Math::BigInt v1.76 in Makefile.PL
	wcr lib: Total: lines 8733, words 30972, chars 222395
	1499 tests ()

=back

=head2 2005-04-18 (Base v3.01 build 2)

=over 2

